<p>Back home there just aint such place as [::1] (thats localhost for all
 of you who dont use BSD). Swinging on the bike and going to the ice dealer,
 the best of them all. It was kind of nice in Switzerland and itll be a hard
 decision for me whether Im going to move there or not. But after arriving
 at home, past the bike tour, I fell into sleep pretty soon. Travelling may
 be interesting, but it sure is tiring.</p>
