@ mksh: update changelog
 mksh: remove an item from todo (base-1 integers are done, base-0 integers
  cant be done but base-1 integers can fulfil the task I had planned for
  them)
 mksh: add an item to wishlist (embedded NULs in strings, for hexdump)
  XXX what about read with timeout or read of single characters?
 wlog: general update
 mksh, wlog: rant about pcc (but IF it works, mkshs now fine with it)
 mksh: add MirOS/i386+pcc to the list of tested operating environments
